This project presents a comprehensive analysis of hotel booking performance using advanced EDA, Power BI dashboarding, DAX measures, and business insights.

It aims to help hotel management:

Maximize revenue efficiency

Identify seasonal booking trends

Understand customer behavior

Improve guest retention

Reduce cancellation losses

Optimize room pricing strategy (ADR)

The dashboard transforms raw booking data into actionable insights that support real-time decision-making.


